# Three.js Journey 🚀

This repository contains my learning progress, experiments, and mini-projects while following the **Three.js Journey** course by **Bruno Simon**.

The goal of this repo is to build a strong foundation in **Three.js**, **WebGL concepts**, and **modern 3D for the web**, through hands-on practice.

---

## 📚 About the Course

**Three.js Journey** is a comprehensive course that covers:
- Three.js fundamentals
- WebGL basics
- Cameras, lights, materials
- Textures & environment maps
- Animations
- Shaders
- Performance optimization
- Real-world 3D scenes

Course by: **Bruno Simon**  
👉 https://threejs-journey.com/

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Three.js**
- **JavaScript (ES6+)**
- **Vite**
- **WebGL**
- **HTML / CSS**

